milestones.description: Stelling and Peter Borren's 76-run partnership is NED's highest for the 8th wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 59 between Stelling and Kervezee
This is the highest match aggregate (412) involving teams Netherlands & Scotland in ODIs
Tim de Leede has broken the record for playing the most ODIs (24) for NED, going past Bas Zuiderent
